        "subtopic": "Classification of Airports",
        "content": "• International Airports → For scheduled international operations, with IATA/ICAO standards.\n\n• Customs Airports → Limited international operations for cargo and charter flights.\n\n• Domestic Airports → Handle only domestic flights, no customs/immigration facilities.\n\n• Civil Enclaves → Civil aviation areas inside defence airfields, managed jointly."
